---
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import PriceCard from "../components/PriceCard.astro";
import QuoteForm from "../components/QuoteForm.astro";
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<style>
  .content-min-h {
    min-height: calc(100vh - 12rem);
  }
</style>

<BaseLayout title="NootSponge - Commissions">
  <main
    class="bg-gradient-to-b from-[#3B2A80] to-[#291e51] text-white w-full flex justify-start items-center flex-col"
  >
    <Header />
    <article
      class="content-min-h mt-12 w-full flex flex-col items-center space-y-12"
    >
      <div class="text-center flex flex-col items-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-[#e7da48] max-w-lg">
          Everyone deserves a place online to call home.
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 max-w-xl">
          Websites are a place to express yourself, provide links to your social
          platforms, or can even be a place to sell things. I'm making that easy
          and affordable for everyone.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-x-6">
        <a
          href="#pricing"
          class="rounded-md bg-[#e7da48] px-3.5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-black shadow-sm hover:bg-yellow-500 focus:outline focus:outline-2 focus:outline-offset-2 focus:outline-yellow-200"
          >Get started</a
        >
        <a href="#process" class="text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-white"
          >Learn more <span aria-hidden="true">â†’</span></a
        >
      </div>
      <div
        id="pricing"
        class="rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-800 to-slate-900 border border-slate-700 w-3/4"
      >
        <div class="space-y-4 m-8">
          <div class="">
            <p class="font-bold text-[#e7da48]">Base Packages</p>
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">
              Affordable for anyone
            </h1>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-row w-full space-x-4">
            <PriceCard tier="Basic" />
            <PriceCard tier="Standard" />
            <PriceCard tier="Premium" />
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-600">
            Does not include domain cost, or hosting cost for the Advanced plan.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id="process" class="w-1/2 space-y-8">
        <div>
          <p class="font-bold text-[#e7da48]">Process</p>
          <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">How it works</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-row justify-between">
          <div class="max-w-md">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight">Quote</h2>
            <p class="leading-6">
              Submit a quote request with the form below. Make sure to give as
              much detail as possible, include colors, shapes, ideas, and any
              reference images. I should get back to you after your quote in
              24-48 hours.
            </p>
          </div>
          <img
            src="/undraw_receipt.svg"
            alt="Reciept Icon"
            class="rounded-3xl p-4 backdrop-brightness-200 float-right shadow-lg shadow-[#3B2A80] border border-slate-700"
            height="25%"
            width="25%"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-row justify-between">
          <img
            src="/undraw_real_time_collaboration.svg"
            alt="Collaboration Icon"
            class="rounded-3xl p-4 backdrop-brightness-200 float-right shadow-lg shadow-[#3B2A80] border border-slate-700"
            height="25%"
            width="25%"
          />
          <div class="max-w-lg">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight">
              Domain &amp; Pre-Commission
            </h2>
            <p class="leading-6">
              Once I have recieved your commission request, I will contact you
              via your preferred method to further discuss your commission. The
              first step will be choosing your domain name and where to register
              it. After that, we will start discussing design and content.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-row justify-between">
          <div class="max-w-lg">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight">Design Phase</h2>
            <p class="leading-6">
              During the design phase, I'll make several drafts of your website
              using Figma. I'll send you a link to the Figma file and you can
              give me feedback on the designs. Once we have a design that you
              like, I'll start building and frameworking the website.
            </p>
          </div>
          <img
            src="/undraw_design_feedback.svg"
            alt="Design Process Icon"
            class="rounded-3xl p-4 backdrop-brightness-200 float-right shadow-lg shadow-[#3B2A80] border border-slate-700"
            height="33%"
            width="33%"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-row justify-between">
          <img
            src="/undraw_web_developer.svg"
            alt="Developer Icon"
            class="rounded-3xl p-4 backdrop-brightness-200 float-right shadow-lg shadow-[#3B2A80] border border-slate-700"
            height="25%"
            width="25%"
          />
          <div class="max-w-lg">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight">Development Phase</h2>
            <p class="leading-6">
              During the development phase, I'll build the website using <a
                href="https://astro.build"
                class="text-[#e7da48] underline transition-colors hover:text-white"
                target="_blank">Astro</a
              >, <a
                href="https://tailwindcss.com"
                class="text-[#e7da48] underline transition-colors hover:text-white"
                target="_blank">Tailwind CSS</a
              >, and <a
                href="https://pages.cloudflare.com/"
                class="text-[#e7da48] underline transition-colors hover:text-white"
                target="_blank">Cloudflare Pages</a
              >. I will send you a link to the development site so you can see
              the progress as I build it.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-row justify-between">
          <div class="max-w-lg">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight">Review</h2>
            <p class="leading-6">
              Once the website is finished, I'll send you a link to the live
              site. You can review the site and make sure everything is working
              as intended. If you find any bugs or issues, I'll fix them as
              quickly as possible. This is the step to ensure it is exactly to
              your liking. Large changes after this point will be subject to
              additional fees. Read the <a
                href="#terms"
                class="text-[#e7da48] underline transition-colors hover:text-white"
                >Terms of Service</a
              > for more information.
            </p>
          </div>
          <img
            src="/undraw_code_review.svg"
            alt="Launch Icon"
            class="rounded-3xl p-4 backdrop-brightness-200 float-right shadow-lg shadow-[#3B2A80] border border-slate-700"
            height="25%"
            width="25%"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id="quote" class="w-full flex flex-col items-center">
        <div class="text-center mb-6">
          <p class="font-bold text-[#e7da48]">Pricing</p>
          <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Request a Quote</h1>
        </div>
        <QuoteForm />
      </div>
      <Footer />
    </article>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
